<h2>International PGP Programs</h2>

The PGP currently enrolls U.S. citizens only. However, we are actively expanding the project with collaborators in countries outside the United States. By registering your interest, along with your country of citizenship, you can help us prioritize our international expansion efforts. We will notify you when more information is available about our international programs.

<% form_for @international_participant do |f| %>

  <p>
    <%= f.label :email, 'E-mail address' %><br />
    <%= f.text_field :email %>
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= f.label :country, 'Country' %><br />
    <%= f.country_select :country %>
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= f.submit "Subscribe" %>
  </p>
<% end %>
